# Quantum Computing Department

## Overview

The Quantum Computing Department focuses on exploring quantum algorithms and their applications to blockchain and cryptography.

## Mission

Advance quantum-resistant cryptography and explore quantum advantages in distributed systems.

## Current Projects

- Quantum key distribution research
- Post-quantum cryptography implementation
- Quantum algorithm optimization
